      "message": "In other places we\u0027ve done,\n\n    float inf \u003d bit_cast\u003cfloat\u003e(0x7f800000);\n    auto scale \u003d if_then_else(1.0f/a \u003c inf, 1.0f/a, 0);\n    r *\u003d scale;\n    g *\u003d scale;\n    b *\u003d scale;\n\nSo, check for 1/a \u003c inf not a \u003d\u003d 0, and if a \u003d\u003d 0, force to 0,0,0,0 anyway.\nPresumably the multiply-by-zero there is unnecessary?  But the 1/a not infinite seems important.",
