      "writtenOn": "2018-06-12T15:46:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Should we compare these out longways?  I remember the inverse of (1,1, 0,0,0,0,0) is not (1,1, 0,0,0,0,0) but something with negative 0\u0027s in there.  They won\u0027t memcmp the same.\n\nOr maybe we canonicalize them in SkColorSpaceXformSteps ctor?",
